Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who had it all,\NPirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His final words spurred people\Nto take to the seas in droves:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've left everything\Nthis world's got to offer {\i1}there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And so men set sail for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, the world is in the midst\Nof the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oars is back on his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to Luffy,\Nbut he dealt plenty of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierna Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather forecast is rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Crank it like mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cranking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes! It's the Super Cold Cannon\Nconnected to the extra-large freezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, push in Oars' stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...Secret Art:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gigant Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go smack Moria awake\Nand make him return our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is almost up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need... a wakeup call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat, how dare you\Ntrash my Thriller Bark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my crew because they were alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But with undead zombies,\NI have nothing to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me, all of the\Nshadows on Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve as my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows Asgard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's collecting all of the shadows\Non the island and absorbing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat, I'd say you absorbed\Naround 100 shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm absorbing 100...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,200!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,300!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,400!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,500!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,600!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,700!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,800!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,900!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000 shadows!
