Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.60,0:07:02.57,Title Card - Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.8\fad(1973,1973)\4a&HFF&}Daybreak on the Nightmarish Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...are inside of Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a load of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doomed. What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as good as dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oars was a pushover for Straw Hat\Nwhen he had 100 shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has ten times that!\NWhere is he storing all of that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's his power, he must have\Nway better control of the ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come too far for\Ncrap like this! It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He even has Straw Hat's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine he has ours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...of his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! This is a lost cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He put a crack in the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion attached to \Nthe mast is collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it! Head for the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over for real this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm gonna vanish!\NMy body is gonna vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Hurry into the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning sun is coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your way to the forest\Nthrough the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave the buildings' shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola, what's keeping you? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, please run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could you say that?\NYou're in the same boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...for this gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't the least bit fazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And here they've lost their shadows as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they still intend to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But all it took was one hit for him\Nto put a crack in the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Moria is way more\Npowerful than Oars ever was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as they intend to fight,\NI'm not leaving this spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we selfishly place our faith\Nin him as the "Star of Hope"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then split as soon \Nas the going gets tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we're no better than lowly insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But this situation is hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As the captain, our obligation\Nwill be met if I stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys... Treasure your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is shining over there!\NHurry into the shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what it means to\Nplace your hope in someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...! Do you want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm either going to live or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care which way the coin flips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never go back to \Nhiding in the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's practically going berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,\NHe doesn't have full control of the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like anger and foolish pride\Nmade him overestimate himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys. We're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna push myself a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of things after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Send him flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! What makes\Nyou think you stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way you'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up against a monster\Nthat's a thousand strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Stop and think for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He even has your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He has your monstrous power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're running out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're here to watch, shut your trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already won the fight with Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it all comes down to finishing\Nthings before the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria plans to use his insane power\Nto buy that brief period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we get obliterated first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will Moria self-destruct first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jet Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The shadows are coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet Bazooka! Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gobs of shadows are being released!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are the shadows leaving\Nif they're under his control?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria is losing control over them\Nas he starts to black out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Moria can't fully control\Na thousand shadows at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Gum-Gum...\N--Brick Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like the punch\Nthat put a crack in the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your baptism!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when a whippersnapper
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,tries to act like a big shot on these waters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you get for defying\None of the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Know your place! The world is devised\Nto crush anyone who stands out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:14:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He got back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if I'm \Na "whippersnapper"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...or if I stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...can...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...crush me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can crush you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability to say that \Nwithout any justification
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,proves just how green you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In just a sec, I'm gonna make you\Nspew out all of the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him? Is he immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Get in the shadows or you're toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! My hand is vanishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry into the shadows!\NThe courtyard isn't safe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it wise to use that\Nattack more than once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember what using\NGear 2 did to you that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your Gum-Gum to shoot yourself over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're here, I'll carry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded by the sea\Nand a bunch of battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stay here, we're gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My body... isn't moving at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! You defeated the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We got Robin back, too!\NAll that's left is for us to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Try hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is nuts, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.46,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...Gigant Jet Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,More shadows are coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let them escape! They're my minions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows, I am your sovereign!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! He doesn't\Nplan on giving up our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Captain Lola!\N--Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My shadow, can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We were always together,\Nclear from the time I was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We came into this world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent the past three years searching\Nfor the zombie that contained you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're in there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can hear me, come back! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hide in the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna turn to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But it's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! Supposedly all of our\Nshadows are currently inside of Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never get another chance like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're up against one\Nof the Seven Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right... Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back! Come back! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say something to my shadow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to become the \NPirate King...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...you had better...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...stick with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat, curse you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare you to go to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The real nightmare awaits\Nyou in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our shadows are coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here come our shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:22:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we take down Moria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like my fears were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not leave witnesses to testify\Nthat Straw Hat defeated Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am assigning you to a special mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Annihilate the entire Straw Hat Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not Out of Danger Yet!\NOrders to Annihilate the Straw Hat Crew"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
